| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2620 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 562c9116-a8b7-51e7-b2e2-bc442f77dc74"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
